  "general_provisions": "This joint resolution of the Utah Legislature proposes to amend the Utah Constitution to modify provisions related to the annual general session.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This resolution:<hr><ltbullet>authorize the Legislature to convene in an annual general session on nonconsecutive days;<hr><ltbullet>require both houses of the Legislature to meet in general session on the same days; and<hr><ltbullet>make conforming changes. ",
